➜爽滑肉嫩东山羊，还弹汁！连汤都不想放过…
http://www.sohu.com/a/428808101_100131509	47358
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201101/58f1ffe395eb4ae08f7c0fa03ec29bf4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">霜降已过，打煲了喂！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">只用海南长大的东山羊，弹汁肉嫩...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">//</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">适合围坐打煲的日子里</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不止鸡，广州人开始对羊下手了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201101/1efda123657f4fe994212c7f9cd189e6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>PART</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 『客家班』上新，羊肉煲打头阵 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201101/1d54a8accccc4efd9d50bc3deabde52e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-justify">打煲是广州人秋冬的第一道仪式感<strong>！</strong>一煲羊肉煲咕噜咕噜上桌，暖粒粒下肚，秋冻冬寒速速退散 ！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>先炒后焖才够味</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>①逼出羊肉香气</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201101/894f0411115f4da29270171f5b13c90c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>②加入竹蔗炖出奶白汤汁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201101/be67f4307f4d4801a013f79dbdb08071.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>③焖煮至软嫩入味</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201101/49f8a46109414f148d9d20209dbeac3c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>东山羊，Q弹软滑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201101/a123da5561b848ccb0e40e9af1277808.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">Q弹胶质的羊皮，<strong>满屏都是胶原蛋白</strong>~咬下去先感受到微粘软糯的皮，汁水紧接着化入口中，羊肉鲜香肆意迸发，越吃越上头~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>客家咸香秘制酱汁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201101/2cdee602f650446dbff3b04ee1dce0ed.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201101/ec0f6db53e10461f89e0905cfc6f2c09.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">羊肉煲常见，但<strong>客家咸香风味</strong>的羊肉煲只能来这吃~炖煮过后酱汁更浓缩了羊肉精华，吃起来真的是<strong>连汤汁都不想放过</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>奶白暖胃猪肚鸡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201101/704aeb2c02414bc4b4f60f4fcac8b9ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">猪肚煲鸡是客家名菜。奶白的浓汤热气滚滚，散发着清新的药材香气，用来<strong>暖胃热身</strong>再合适不过。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201101/0d01e294eb704a50b29a2f3a27455c47.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201101/dbb56466e1bd4675ad554a91eb9151ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201101/b1c9630597654a7d9aa18fa0459ef548.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">先喝一口汤暖胃，<strong>汤水清甜</strong>，带有些微胡椒的热辣，瞬间唤醒味蕾。再慢慢品味<strong>细滑肉嫩的</strong>鸡肉和<strong>爽脆弹牙</strong>的猪肚，一锅下肚超满足！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>这道焖鹅，海味加持</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201101/1934cfa7bb224719ab5ee7047b4391b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这一道焖鹅牌面十足，要各式海鲜来给它做配角？<strong>鲜甜海味和鹅香竟然超match</strong>，喜欢吃鹅的小伙伴不能错过这个神仙吃法～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201101/13e83cb3b542403e87d65067b040754b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201101/61a1d1f6eaf14d779e52e7480c85c2e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201101/dd7ee8811713460cabcaf42fcd263aad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201101/7250b4ca38a14c759045e9d2769bdff9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鹅肉<strong>皮香肉滑</strong>，带有浓郁的酱香味，咬一口满口油香！鲜虾、蟹肉、白贝<strong>饱吸汤汁，又不失鲜味</strong>，吃起来很上头，筷子完全停不下来...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>PART</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 还有这些，都是地道客家味 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>上桌现焗鲟龙鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201101/7b58f19540554c24ace9a613404e7c6a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鲟龙鱼因营养价值丰富被称为“鱼中贵族”。<strong>上桌现焗，开盖即食</strong>，美味完全没有延时~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201101/ff1b6db172a041bc9375505d32cb9cf3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201101/38406c29680848f79b64a06bcda7f81e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201101/fb851c2cc88740a1a7ad152e1b6bb3e1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一揭盖，鱼肉清香夹杂蒜香扑鼻而来，勾人食指大动...<strong>新鲜现焗</strong>的鱼肉滑熘熘，夹都夹不住。肉多无刺，吃起来<strong>爽滑鲜嫩，回味悠长...</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>香烤孜然羊排</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201101/059b4c6c441f4a17a53efb960a87268b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">烤羊排的皮脂烤制得微焦，<strong>泛着诱人的金黄光泽</strong>，孜然香气的加持，更能刺激食欲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201101/749d1ab17acc4fa8acdf92c5c0985a88.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201101/70b6b46f6fef46e2a4760ce211615828.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">羊排撕着吃才过瘾！皮肉顺着油脂层与细嫩的肉质纤维分离，香气渐渐洋溢...趁热咬上一大口，<strong>汁水迸发，肉香喷涌而出</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>椒香鲜辣牛百猪肚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201101/f60b1ff185294c62ac9d25a455f4a486.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201101/0c43b68c76ad448f981dd68a0cf9ad2c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201101/1743f34ad6dc4444a4fbc6235826f02a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>牛百叶爽脆筋道、猪肚肥厚Q弹</strong>，经过鲜椒汤底的炖煮，丝毫没有腥味。入口<strong>微微麻辣</strong>，吃起来很开胃~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>嫩滑清香酿凉瓜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201101/151eb74cd14d457897dbed6586170f08.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201101/f1d991c5ce9945748f7fdda702d8eea1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201101/43b359998fcb45d7a358ea1da12aabe5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">客家人料理起酿菜可谓是得心应手。这道酿凉瓜是<strong>“煎酿三宝”之一</strong>，嫩滑清香，尝起来软糯不油腻，可以说是老少皆宜~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>03</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>PART</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一店一景，搬来了客家园林</strong></p>
