<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201101/dddf4c1ced7e4b74a2fe1ef9e671a5e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>秋冬来这打煲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201101/ccc1c820ebc64de1871eb681b974daa1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
